trans-unit.id: Our system works on the principle of an exchange: all offers for sale and purchase are formed by our users.
trans-unit.source: Our system works on the principle of an exchange: all offers for sale and purchase are generated by our users. Users are guaranteed to be offered the most profitable of the options for buying and selling. The system does not guarantee that a better offer will not appear after the transaction.

trans-unit.id: Any user can sell any item in his inventory. Listing an item for sale

trans-unit.target: Cualquier usuario puede vender cualquier artículo de su inventario. Poner un artículo a la venta no da como resultado la pérdida de un artículo del inventario de Steam, sino que solo indica que desea vender este artículo.

trans-unit.id: After the buyer pays for the purchase, the seller will have to transfer the necessary item to our system within 5 minutes.
trans-unit.source: After the buyer pays for the purchase, the seller will have to transfer the necessary item to our system within 5 minutes. If the item is transferred, the transaction is considered completed, if the item is not transferred within 5 minutes, the transaction is canceled. It is impossible to cancel the transaction before reaching 5 minutes.
trans-unit.target: Después de que el comprador pague la compra, el vendedor deberá transferir el artículo necesario a su sistema en 5 minutos. Si se transfiere el artículo, la transacción se considera completada, si el artículo no se transfiere en 5 minutos, la transacción se cancela. Es imposible cancelar la transacción antes de llegar a los 5 minutos.
